{"id":14070,"date":"2024-02-14T10:12:04","date_gmt":"2024-02-14T07:12:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/alerjidiyetisyenin.com\/?p=14070"},"modified":"2024-02-14T10:12:04","modified_gmt":"2024-02-14T07:12:04","slug":"kabzilik-nedir","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/alerjidiyetisyenin.com\/kabzilik-nedir\/","title":{"rendered":"Kabz\u0131l\u0131k Nedir?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Kab\u0131zl\u0131k ba\u011f\u0131rsakta bulunan kas dokusunun tamamen gev\u015feyememesinden kaynaklanan, ba\u011f\u0131rsaklar\u0131n tam bo\u015falmamas\u0131 durumudur.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Kab\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n artt\u0131\u011f\u0131 durumlar:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u00d6zellikle kad\u0131nlarda hamilelik d\u00f6neminde veya do\u011fumdan sonra s\u0131kl\u0131kla g\u00f6r\u00fclebilmektedir.<\/p>\n<p>Ya\u015fl\u0131larda, lifli g\u0131dalardan fakir beslenenlerde, kullan\u0131lan ila\u00e7 ve takviyelere ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak kab\u0131zl\u0131k \u015fikayeti artmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>Sindirim sisteminin farkl\u0131 organlar\u0131ndaki sa\u011fl\u0131k sorunlar\u0131na sahip ki\u015filerde kab\u0131zl\u0131k g\u00f6r\u00fclme olas\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 artmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<h2 id='kab\u0131z-oldu\u011fumuzu-nas\u0131l-anlar\u0131z' ><strong>Kab\u0131z Oldu\u011fumuzu Nas\u0131l Anlar\u0131z?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Kab\u0131zl\u0131k teriminin farkl\u0131 insanlar i\u00e7in farkl\u0131 anlamlar\u0131 bulunmaktad\u0131r. Baz\u0131 hastalar i\u00e7in d\u0131\u015fk\u0131 \u00e7ok sert ve k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck olabilirken, ba\u015fka bir hasta i\u00e7in d\u0131\u015fk\u0131n\u0131n \u00e7ok zor ve seyrek yap\u0131lmas\u0131 \u015feklinde olabilmektedir.<\/p>\n<p><strong>En S\u0131k G\u00f6r\u00fclen Belirtiler:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>D\u0131\u015fk\u0131lama Esnas\u0131nda Zorlanmak<\/li>\n<li>D\u0131\u015fk\u0131 Miktar\u0131n\u0131n Azalmas\u0131 (Ba\u011f\u0131rsa\u011f\u0131 Tamamen Bo\u015faltamamak)<\/li>\n<li>D\u0131\u015fk\u0131n\u0131n Topakl\u0131 Ve Sert Olmas\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Anorektal T\u0131kanma Hissi<\/li>\n<li>D\u0131\u015fk\u0131lama \u0130\u00e7in Parmak Manevralar\u0131na \u0130htiya\u00e7 Duyma<\/li>\n<li>Haftada 3\u2019ten Az Kendi Kendine Ba\u011f\u0131rsak Bo\u015falmas\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Laksatif \u0130la\u00e7lara Ve Takviyelere \u0130htiya\u00e7 Duymak.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Bu belirtiler 3 ay boyunca devaml\u0131 g\u00f6r\u00fcl\u00fcyorsa kab\u0131zl\u0131k ile ilgili beslenme deste\u011fi almal\u0131s\u0131n\u0131z.<\/p>\n<h3 id='kab\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n-nedenleri' ><strong>Kab\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n Nedenleri<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Liften Fakir Beslenmek<\/li>\n<li>Yeterli Mikatrda Su T\u00fcketmemek<\/li>\n<li>Fiziksel Aktivitelerden Yoksunluk<\/li>\n<li>\u00c7\u00f6lyak Hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Multipl Skleroz<\/li>\n<li>Parkinson Hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Diyabet<\/li>\n<li>Hipotiroid<\/li>\n<li>Dengesiz Laksatif Kullan\u0131m\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Antidepresanlar<\/li>\n<li>Anoreksia Nervoza<\/li>\n<li>Irr\u0131tabl Ba\u011f\u0131rsak Sendromu<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id='kab\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n-tedavisi' ><strong>Kab\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n Tedavisi<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Basit karbonhidratlardan uzak durmal\u0131, kompleks karbonhifratlar t\u00fcketmelisiniz.<\/p>\n<p>Beyaz ekmek yerine tam tah\u0131ll\u0131, \u00e7avdar veya siyez unlu ekmekler<\/p>\n<p>Pirin\u00e7, bulgur pilav\u0131 yerine kinoa, karabu\u011fday t\u00fcketebilirsiniz.<\/p>\n<p>Meyve ve sebzelerden zengin beslenerek v\u00fccudunuzun ihtiyac\u0131 olan lifi almal\u0131s\u0131n\u0131z.<\/p>\n<p>G\u00fcnde 2 porsiyon meyve 3 porsiyon taze ve mevsimine uygun sebzeler t\u00fcketebilirsiniz.<\/p>\n<p>G\u00fcnl\u00fck kilo x 35 ml su t\u00fcketmelisiniz.<\/p>\n<p>Haftada en az 3-4 g\u00fcn ak\u015fam yeme\u011finden sonra 30- 40 dakikal\u0131k y\u00fcr\u00fcy\u00fc\u015fler yapabilrsiniz.<\/p>\n<p>Gerekmedik\u00e7e laksatif kullanmay\u0131n.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Kab\u0131zl